rtak Moscow]] in the [[2012\u201313 Russian Cup]] game against [[FC Salyut Belgorod]] on 26 September 2012.<ref>{{Cite web|publisher=[[Russian Premier League]]|url=https://eng.premierliga.ru/match/match_8976.html|title=Salyut v Spartak game report|date=26 September 2012}}</ref>\n\nHe made his [[Russian Premier League]] debut for [[FC Amkar Perm]] on 30 August 2013 in a game against [[PFC CSKA Moscow]].\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerway|nikolay-fadeev/269437}}\n* {{FootballFacts.ru|29184-fadeev-nikolaj-petrovich}}\n* {{RPL player|Fadeev-Nikolay}}\n* [http://news.sportbox.ru/Vidy_sporta/Futbol/stats/man_1270745170 Player page by sportbox.ru] {{dead link|date=April 2020}} {{in lang|ru}}\n* {{Sportbox.ru|Futbol/Nikolay-Petrovich-Fadeev-Futbol-09051993}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Fadeyev, Nikolai}}\n[[Category:1993 births]]\n[[Category:People from Ulyanovsk]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Russian footballers]]\n[[Category:Russia youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:FC Spartak Moscow players]]\n[[Category:FC Amkar Perm players]]\n[[Category:Russian Premier League players]]\n[[Category:FC Khimki players]]\n[[Category:FC Torpedo Moscow players]]\n[[Category:FC SKA-Khabarovsk players]]\n\n\n{{Russia-footy-defender-1993-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Russian professional football player|bot=PearBOT 5}}\n{{Eastern Slavic name|Petrovich|Fadeyev}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name= Nikolai Fadeyev\n| fullname = Nikolai Petrovich Fadeyev\n| image = Nikolai Fadeyev 2017.jpg\n| caption = Fadeyev with Torpedo Moscow in 2017\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1993|5|9|df=yes}} \n| birth_place = [[Ulyanovsk]], [[Russia]]\n| height = {{height|m=1.79}}\n| currentclub = \n| clubnumber = \n| position = [[Defender (football)|Defender]]\n| youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = \n| years1 = 2010\u20132016 | clubs1 = [[FC Spartak Moscow]]      | caps1 =  0 | goals1 = 0  \n| years2 = 2013     