sen]]}}\n| extra10 = Kurstin\n| length10 = 4:33\n| title11 = [[Love Me Anyway (Pink song)|Love Me Anyway]]\n| note11 = featuring [[Chris Stapleton]]\n| writer11 = {{hlist|Pink|[[Allen Shamblin]]|[[Tom Douglas (songwriter)|Tom Douglas]]}}\n| extra11 = {{hlist|Pink|Sal Oliveri{{ref|a|[a]}}|Simon Gooding{{ref|a|[a]}}}}\n| length11 = 3:08\n| title12 = Circle Game\n| writer12 = {{hlist|Pink|Kurstin}}\n| extra12 = Kurstin\n| length12 = 4:54\n| title13 = The Last Song of Your Life\n| writer13 = {{hlist|Pink|[[Billy Mann]]}}\n| extra13 = {{hlist|Mann|Pink}}\n| length13 = 3:53\n| all_writing = \n}}\n{{Track listing\n| collapsed       = yes\n| headline        = ''Hurts 2B Human''{{nobold|&nbsp;\u2013 Japan bonus track}}<ref>{{cite web|title=\u3010CD\u3011\u30d3\u30e5\u30fc\u30c6\u30a3\u30d5\u30eb\u30fb\u30c8\u30e9\u30a6\u30de\uff1c\u521d\u56de\u9650\u5b9a\u4ed5\u69d8\uff1eAlbum|url=http://www.cdjapan.co.jp/product/SICP-6087?s_ssid=e370175ca5ae69dbf3|website=CD Japan|location=Japan|accessdate=April 3, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404101333/http://www.cdjapan.co.jp/product/SICP-6087?s_ssid=e370175ca5ae69dbf3|archive-date=April 4, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| extra_column    = Producer(s)\n| total_length    =\n\n| title14         = More\n| writer14        = {{hlist|Pink|Jetta John-Hartley|[[busbee]]}}\n| length14        = 3:50\n}}\n'''Notes'''\n* {{small|{{note|a|a}}}} signifies an additional producer\n* {{small|{{note|b|b}}}} signifies a vocal producer\n\n==Personnel==\nCredits adapted from the liner notes of ''Hurts 2B Human''.<ref name=\"credits\">{{cite AV media notes|title=Hurts 2B Human|others=[[Pink (singer)|Pink]]|year=2019|publisher=[[RCA Records]]}}</ref>\n\n===Performers and musicians===\n{{div col}}\n* [[Pink (singer)|Pink]] \u2013 vocals, background vocals (2, 9)\n* [[Wrabel]] \u2013 featured vocals {{small|(5)}}\n* [[Khalid (singer)|Khalid]] \u2013  featured vocals {{small|(6)}}\n* [[Chris Stapleton]] \u2013 featured vocals {{small|(11)}}\n*